<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Our Vision</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #4f46e5 50%, #4338ca 100%);
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .clouds {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 25% 25%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 20%, transparent 21%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 75% 35%, rgba(255,255,255,0.08) 25%, transparent 26%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 45% 75%, rgba(255,255,255,0.12) 18%, transparent 19%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 85%, rgba(255,255,255,0.06) 30%, transparent 31%);
            animation: float 30s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px) rotate(0deg); }
            25% { transform: translateY(-20px) rotate(0.5deg); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px) rotate(-0.5deg); }
            75% { transform: translateY(-25px) rotate(0.3deg); }
        }
        
        .content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            padding: 60px 50px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            max-width: 800px;
            z-index: 2;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .icon {
            font-size: 4.5em;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 25px 0;
            font-size: 3.2em;
            font-weight: 700;
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ffffff, #e0e7ff);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }
        
        .subtitle {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            margin: 0 0 35px 0;
            opacity: 0.9;
            font-weight: 400;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .vision-points {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .vision-point {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 35px 30px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            text-align: left;
        }
        
        .point-icon {
            font-size: 2.8em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: block;
        }
        
        .point-title {
            font-size: 1.4em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: #e0e7ff;
        }
        
        .point-desc {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        
        .global-impact {
            margin-top: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 18px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
        }
        
        .impact-title {
            font-size: 1.6em;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #e0e7ff;
        }
        
        .impact-stats {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .stat {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .stat-icon {
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .stat-text {
            font-size: 1.1em;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 40px 30px;
            }
            h1 {
                font-size: 2.5em;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="clouds"></div>
    <div class="content">
        <span class="icon">üåç</span>
        <h1>Our Vision</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Creating a world where food waste is eliminated and hunger is a thing of the past through technology and community collaboration</p>
        
        <div class="vision-points">
            <div class="vision-point">
                <span class="point-icon">üöÄ</span>
                <div class="point-title">Global Network</div>
                <div class="point-desc">Building a worldwide network of food sharing that connects communities and transforms surplus food into valuable resources</div>
            </div>
            <div class="vision-point">
                <span class="point-icon">üí°</span>
                <div class="point-title">Innovation</div>
                <div class="point-desc">Leveraging cutting-edge technology to make food donation simple, efficient, and impactful for everyone involved</div>
            </div>
            <div class="vision-point">
                <span class="point-icon">ü§ù</span>
                <div class="point-title">Community</div>
                <div class="point-desc">Fostering strong community bonds by bringing together businesses, organizations, and individuals around a common cause</div>
            </div>
            <div class="vision-point">
                <span class="point-icon">üå±</span>
                <div class="point-title">Sustainability</div>
                <div class="point-desc">Promoting environmental sustainability by reducing food waste and its impact on our planet's resources</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="global-impact">
            <div class="impact-title">Our Global Impact Goals</div>
            <div class="impact-stats">
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-icon">üçΩÔ∏è</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">1M+ Meals Saved</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-icon">üåç</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Zero Food Waste</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-icon">üë•</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Communities United</div>
                </div>
                <div class="stat">
                    <div class="stat-icon">üíö</div>
                    <div class="stat-text">Sustainable Future</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
